<span style="color: #000000;"> </span><br /><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">                      <span style="font-size: xx-large;">《空山望月》丝竹音乐会</span></span></strong></span><br /><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">                              <br />                                                 时间：2012年10月12日 晚19点30分</span></strong></span><br /><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                                地点：民族音乐厅<br />                                                     主持人：王军（国家一级演员）</span></strong></span><br /><br /><br /><br />
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(一)   丝竹乐合奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《欢乐歌》                                                                                传统乐曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《咏南》                                                                                        朱毅曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(二)   笛子与琵琶</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《中花六板》                                                                             传统乐曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">               演奏：王次恒（国家一级演员）  董晓琳（中国音乐金钟奖获得者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(三)   扬琴独奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《弹词三六》                                                                             传统乐曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                 演奏：袁可（全国民族器乐邀请赛金奖获得者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(四)   笙独奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《微山湖船歌》                                                                          牟善平曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      演奏：吴学伟（中国音乐金钟奖获得者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(五)   古筝独奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《﻿高山流水》                                                                             浙江筝曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《浪淘沙》                                                                             邱大成改编</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                         演奏：张璐 </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(六)   二胡独奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《江南春色》                                                                             朱昌躍曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《远方的客人请你留下来》                                                 严浩敏编曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                           演奏：詹丽君（文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获得者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(七)   琵琶独奏 </span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《春江花月夜》                                                                                 古曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《龙船》                                                                                     华彦钧曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                        演奏：董晓琳</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(八)   笛子与二胡</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《女人花》                                                              陈耀川曲   姜莹改编</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                             演奏：丁晓逵（CCTV民乐大赛获奖者）  蒋倩</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(九)   笛子独奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《桑园春》                                                                                 王次恒曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演奏：王次恒</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">(十)   丝竹乐合奏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《行街》                                                                                     传统乐曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">         《绿染江南》                                                       王次恒曲  杨春林配器</span></p>
